e/Olympic_Glory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My wife's Aunt by marriage was from Scotland and knew Eric Liddell both in Scotland and as a fellow missionary in China.\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3614, \"end\": 3622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"score\": 0.9906188618198566, \"rank\": 0.007172047667472744, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\"}, {\"begin\": 3632, \"end\": 3644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.914739618712637e-65, \"text\": \"Eric Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\"}, {\"begin\": 3653, \"end\": 3661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"score\": 0.9906188618198566, \"rank\": 0.007172047667472744, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\"}, {\"begin\": 3692, \"end\": 3697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_China\", \"score\": 0.9017873724459956, \"rank\": 0.10885448401637698, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My wife's Aunt\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3592}, {\"ngram\": \"marriage\", \"from\": 3596, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"a fellow missionary\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She lived to 100 and often talked to me about how Eric was such a selfless, giving man.\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eric\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3753}, {\"ngram\": \"man\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He died in 1945 at the age of 43 in a Japanese concentration camp in China where he and so many expatriates were imprisoned.\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3825, \"end\": 3833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9988069763597346, \"rank\": 0.001134120551264783, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3856, \"end\": 3861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_China\", \"score\": 0.9017873724459956, \"rank\": 0.10885448401637698, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3813}, {\"ngram\": \"so many expatriates\", \"from\": 3875, \"to\": 3894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he kept on doing his duty.\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his duty\", \"from\": 3933, \"to\": 3941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He organised competitive sport (even on a Sunday) as recreation for the inmates.\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 4023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitive sport\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 3973}, {\"ngram\": \"a Sunday\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3991}, {\"ngram\": \"recreation\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4006}, {\"ngram\": \"the inmates\", \"from\": 4011, \"to\": 4022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When he was asked why he did that he answered that he was doing his duty because God knew these vulnerable kids in the camp needed it and Sunday was their only day free from work.\", \"from\": 4024, \"to\": 4203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his duty\", \"from\": 4088, \"to\": 4096}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 4105, \"to\": 4108}, {\"ngram\": \"these vulnerable kids\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4135}, {\"ngram\": \"t